            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2o0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">The establishment of the office of historian,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">its origins are quite ancient.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">In the past, when the Yellow Emperor received his mandate,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">Cangjie and Juju were in fact holding these positions.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">As for the Three Dynasties,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">their number gradually increased.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">According to the *Zhou Guan* (Rites of Zhou) and the *Li Ji* (Book of Rites),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">there were names such as Grand Historian, Minor Historian, Inner Historian, Outer Historian, Left Historian, and Right Historian.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">The Grand Historian was in charge of the six canons of the state,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">the Minor Historian was in charge of the records of the states,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">the Inner Historian was in charge of writing the king's orders,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">the Outer Historian was in charge of writing communications to the four directions,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">the Left Historian recorded speeches,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">the Right Historian recorded events.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">The *Qu Li* (Book of Rites) says:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">"The historian carries a writing brush;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">important matters are recorded on bamboo slips,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">minor matters are simply recorded on wooden tablets."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">The *Da Dai Li* (Record of Rituals by Dai the Elder) says:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">"When the crown prince has been capped and becomes an adult,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">and is released from the care of tutors and guardians,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-3a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">then there are historians who record his transgressions."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">The *Han Shi Wai Zhuan* (Han Ying's Illustrations of the Book of Songs) says:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">"The one who adheres to the law, guards his position, and dares not do wrong is</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">the Grand Historian."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">Thus, the creation of the office of historian</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">began with the Yellow Emperor,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">was fully established in the Zhou dynasty,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">the titles were numerous,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">and the duties were all different.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">As for the feudal lords and the various states,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">they also each had historians,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">and when it came to their positions and titles,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_037-4a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-25T11:28:54.857+09:00">they were the same as the king's.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
